  robot.respond /(do|does) (I|he|she|they) give a fuck|how much (do|does) (I|he|she|they) care|how (many|much) fucks (do|does) (I|he|she|they) give|(do|does) (I|he|she|they) (look like (I|he|she|they))? give a fuck/i, (msg) ->
        msg.send msg.random response
